'''《無盡的玩笑》'''（{{lang-en|''Infinite Jest''}}），是[[美國|美國]]作家[[大衛·福斯特·華萊士|大衛·福斯特·華萊士]]於1996年創作的[[小說|小說]]。該小說以非常規的敘事結構與大量的註腳聞名。它被歸類為{{link-en|百科全書小說|Encyclopedic novel}}，並被[[時代雜誌|《時代》雜誌]]列入1923年至2005年出版的100部最佳英語小說清單。<ref name="Time">{{Cite news | last = Grossman | first = Lev | last2 = Lacayo | first2 = Richard | title = TIME's Critics pick the 100 Best Novels, 1923 to present | newspaper = TIME | url = http://entertainment.time.com/2005/10/16/all-time-100-novels/slide/infinite-jest-1996-by-david-foster-wallace/ | date = 16 October 2005 | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archive-date = 2021-03-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210321223412/https://entertainment.time.com/2005/10/16/all-time-100-novels/slide/infinite-jest-1996-by-david-foster-wallace/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>1996年逢出版便售出44,000份精裝本<ref>{{cite web|last1=Holub|first1=Christian|title=Infinite Jest, 20 years later|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/02/26/infinite-jest-20th-anniversary|access-date=2020-09-24|archive-date=2018-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717183918/http://ew.com/article/2016/02/26/infinite-jest-20th-anniversary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，目前全球銷量已突破一百萬。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Winter|first1=Infinite|title=Michael Pietsch Interview|url=http://infinitewinter.org/michael-pietsch-interview/|date=2016-04-06|access-date=2020-09-24|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122121334/http://infinitewinter.org/michael-pietsch-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

